title: Automobile Tire Pneumatic Casings, Production for United States
notes:
Data Were Raised To Total Industry On Basis Of Bienniel Census Of Manufacturers' Reports. Some Data Misprinted In Sources Were Checked And Corrected By NBER. Source: Received Direct From National Rubber Manufacturers' Association, But Data May Also Be Found In Survey Of Current Business, May 1939, P.16 And Issues For 1955.
